:: FirstClient {"position":"275,150","size":"100,100"}
You arrive at your first client: a soccer-van coated in the trifecta: goldfish, dog glitter ("fur"), and mystery stickiness.

(if: $transport is 2)[
Your motorcycle backpack held: one microfiber, one bottle of APC, and optimism.
The van laughs in Cheerios.
Client: "Can you also shampoo the headliner and fix my son’s slime sculpture?"
You quote bravely, but this might take longer.
(set: $job_ok to 0)
(set: $gain to 10)(display: "AwardXP")
]
(else:)[
You unload the full ATD kit like a magician pulling gear from a hat.
Foam cannon sings. The van confesses its sins. You restore honor to the minivan clan.
(set: $job_ok to 1)
(set: $gain to 25)(display: "AwardXP")
]

