:: MorningRoutine {"position":"650,25","size":"100,100"}
You wake up to your alarm labeled: "BE A RESPONSIBLE ADULT".

Do you:

* [[Shower like a professional human->MorningChoice1]]
* [[Blast some deodorant and call it 'Speed Shower™'->MorningChoice2]]


:: OutbreakIntro {"position":"525,275","size":"100,100"}
As you’re finishing up, you notice three things:
* Your phone pings with a news alert: "PLEASE DO NOT PANIC but also maybe panic".
* A man across the street is chasing a mailman while trying to bite envelopes.
* The dog you just de-furred says "braaaiiins" (probably).

(if: $cleanliness is 1)[
Good news: you smell fantastic. If zombies hunt by scent, they’ll pick the Speed-Shower guy.
]
(else:)[
You smell intriguing. Zombies are foodies now.
]

(if: $transport is 3)[
You consider running away. You are already running, technically.
]

(if: $job_ok is 1)[
The client, grateful, offers you a tip… in canned beans. "These might be currency soon."
]
(else:)[
The client asks if the apocalypse includes a discount. You pretend the foam cannon is a fire hose and leave.
]

(if: $supplies >= 2)[
Thanks to your supply stop, you jury-rig a quick door barricade / hose-lasso.
]
(else-if: $supplies is 1)[
Your supplies aren’t glamorous, but they help. You hand a donut to a non-zombie. Morale +1.
]
(else:)[
You have… water. Which is good. Hydration is important when fleeing politely.
]

A lone zombie shuffles toward the freshly detailed van, admiring the beading.

To be continued…

